73		 * candidates are stored in files named
74		 * {@code META-INF/spring/full-qualified-annotation-name.imports} on the classpath.
75		 * Every line contains the full qualified name of the candidate class. Comments are
76		 * supported using the # character.
77		 * @param annotation annotation to load
78		 * @param classLoader class loader to use for loading
79		 * @return list of names of annotated classes
